sources.description:
The Adventure of Two Lifetimes.
A mysterious drifter bonds with a boy with tales of the West. Past and present collide when a lawman appears seeking long-lost gold.

Original title: The Legend of 5 Mile Cave (2019) 


Director: Brent Christy
Writers: Dustin Rikert, William Shockley
Stars: Adam Baldwin, Jeremy Sumpter, Jill Wagner
Genres: Action, Adventure, Western movie


00:00 Full Movie (with subtitles).
08:22 A captivating book leads to unexpected adventures in the Wild West.
14:39 Exploring the tale of Shooter Green and his legendary stagecoach robbery in the Wild West.
20:53 A sharpshooter impresses a crowd with his skills and catches the attention of a mysterious woman.
26:57 Secret love between Josie and Shooter hindered by societal expectations and financial constraints.
33:28 Farm faces foreclosure after owner's passing, despite efforts to save it.
38:57 Shooter contemplates proposing to Josie but needs money for an engagement ring, leading him to stay put instead of moving on.
44:57 A secret wedding ceremony takes place between Josie and Sam, officiated by a pastor.

56:58 Plans to spread a false story about a shootout to cover up their crime.
1:03:34 Bud rents a room in a boarding house run by Susan and Mr. Tabor.
1:11:30 Confrontation between two characters over missing gold and escape from captivity in a western setting.
1:15:54 A grandfather heroically saves his family from a dangerous foe in a Western action scene.
